comments: Mrs. C wants you to be successful . Learned a lot about how my attitude was holding me back. I can see now how my choices need to be toward my goals. I thought I was too smart for this course but what I learned was how my mindset was preventing me from achieving my best work. She holds you to the work and pushes you to give her your best.

comments: Carol Carter is a very caring, compassionate counselor and professor, who truly cares about her students tremendously. She will go out of her way to help any student that will make the effort to help themselves 1st. Carol is a perfect role model for the type of empathy and understanding that more teachers need to display. Excellent overall!
